"{\"uid\": \"leadership.ng-ralph-lauren-chooses-blue-jeans-for-team-usas-olympic-uniforms\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Ralph Lauren -who has dressed Team USA at nine consecutive Olympics and Paralympics- has unveiled Tuesday his latest creations for the athletes who will represent the country at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 197, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 12, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"score\": 0.9987116473983306, \"rank\": 0.0012900145954046975, \"text\": \"Ralph Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\"}, {\"begin\": 30, \"end\": 38, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9970234608999411, \"rank\": 0.002901236833137449, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nine consecutive Olympics\", \"from\": 42, \"to\": 67}, {\"ngram\": \"Paralympics-\", \"from\": 72, \"to\": 84}, {\"ngram\": \"his latest creations\", \"from\": 106, \"to\": 126}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 131, \"to\": 143}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 163, \"to\": 174}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 178, \"to\": 196}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the opening ceremony on the Seine, the designer has opted to outfit the Olympians in a classic navy Ralph Lauren blazer with red and white detailing, paired with a striped Oxford shirt, navy knit tie, and tapered light denim jeans.\", \"from\": 198, \"to\": 433, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 230, \"end\": 235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9992672771367729, \"rank\": 0.0007201039553613877, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 374, \"end\": 386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dress_shirt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Oxford shirt\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dress_shirt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dress_shirt\"}, {\"begin\": 421, \"end\": 426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denim\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"denim\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denim\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denim\"}, {\"begin\": 427, \"end\": 432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"jeans\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 202, \"to\": 222}, {\"ngram\": \"the designer\", \"from\": 237, \"to\": 249}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympians\", \"from\": 270, \"to\": 283}, {\"ngram\": \"a classic navy\", \"from\": 287, \"to\": 301}, {\"ngram\": \"red and white detailing\", \"from\": 327, \"to\": 350}, {\"ngram\": \"navy\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 392}]}, {\"sentence\": \"David Lauren, the company's chief branding and innovation officer, and its founder's son, was unbothered by the casualness of blue denim.\", \"from\": 435, \"to\": 572, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 435, \"end\": 447, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Lauren\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Lauren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Lauren\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the company's chief branding and innovation officer\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 500}, {\"ngram\": \"its founder's son\", \"from\": 506, \"to\": 523}, {\"ngram\": \"the casualness\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 557}, {\"ngram\": \"blue denim\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 571}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We work very closely with Team USA to make the athletes feel at once dressed up, feel like a team, but at the same time comfortable and very distinctively American,\\\" he told The Associated Press on Monday during a media preview at the company's posh New York headquarters.\", \"from\": 574, \"to\": 847, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 601, \"end\": 609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9970234608999411, \"rank\": 0.002901236833137449, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}, {\"begin\": 753, \"end\": 769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999997827469779, \"rank\": 1.8959310377906517e-07, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 825, \"end\": 833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999429512644, \"rank\": 4.676797339408453e-08, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 630}, {\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 672}, {\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 681, \"to\": 694}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 779}, {\"ngram\": \"a media preview\", \"from\": 787, \"to\": 802}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Nothing says America like blue jeans,\\\" Lauren added.\", \"from\": 847, \"to\": 900, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nothing\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 855}, {\"ngram\": \"America\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 868}, {\"ngram\": \"blue jeans\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 884}, {\"ngram\": \"Lauren\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 893}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Daniela Moroz, competing in sailing at her first Olympics, said she loved the racing details of the closing look she modelled for the launch, down to the shoes.\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 1062, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 902, \"end\": 909, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniela_Alves_Lima\", \"score\": 0.9990517499846682, \"rank\": 0.0005328073190288336, \"text\": \"Daniela\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniela_Alves_Lima\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniela_Alves_Lima\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sailing\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 937}, {\"ngram\": \"her first Olympics\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 959}, {\"ngram\": \"the racing details\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 994}, {\"ngram\": \"the closing look\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1014}, {\"ngram\": \"the launch\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1042}, {\"ngram\": \"the shoes\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1061}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paralympic swimmer Jamal Hill was also a fan of the closing ceremony outfit.\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1139, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1063, \"end\": 1081, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Para_swimming\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paralympic swimmer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Para_swimming\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Para_swimming\"}, {\"begin\": 1082, \"end\": 1087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamal_Lyon\", \"score\": 0.9999988960163774, \"rank\": 1.0293050885163838e-06, \"text\": \"Jamal\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamal_Lyon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamal_Lyon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fan\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1107}, {\"ngram\": \"the closing ceremony outfit\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1138}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To him, it's a combination of \\\"cowboy tuxedo\\\" vibes and Formula 1 style.\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1212, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a combination\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1166}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"cowboy tuxedo\\\" vibes\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1191}, {\"ngram\": \"Formula 1 style\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1211}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am a racer on the water so that really speaks to me,\\\" said Moroz, who was born and raised in the San Francisco Bay Area, of the moto touches.\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1358, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a racer\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1227}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1240}, {\"ngram\": \"Moroz\", \"from\": 1276, \"to\": 1281}, {\"ngram\": \"the San Francisco Bay Area\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1336}, {\"ngram\": \"the moto touches\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1357}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's super comfortable.\\\"\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1384, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will definitely be wearing it outside the Paralympic Village,\\\" Hill added.\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1463, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paralympic Village\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1449}, {\"ngram\": \"Hill\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1456}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While Ralph Lauren has the opening and closing ceremonies covered, Nike is outfitting athletes for the medal ceremonies and Team USA medallists will sport blue zip-up jackets and stretchy tapered pants.\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1667, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1471, \"end\": 1483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"score\": 0.9987116473983306, \"rank\": 0.0012900145954046975, \"text\": \"Ralph Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\"}, {\"b